high_descs: Move to the desk behind you
Pick up a pen from the desk
Move to the left side of the desk
Put the pen in a cup on the desk
Pick up the cup from the desk
Move to the middle of the desk
Put the cup on the desk
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a pen on a desk.

high_descs: Turn around to face the table.
Pick up the pen from off of the table.
Turn left and back to the table.
Put the pen in the mug on the table.
Pick up the mug and pen from the table.
Move right a little bit.
Set the mug and pen back on the table near the book.
anns.task_desc: Put the pen in the mug and set it on the table near the book.

high_descs: Turn around to face the desk.
Pick up the pen on the desk, to the right of the mug
Turn left, move forward, and turn right to face the desk again.
Put the pen in the mug, on the desk.
Pick up the mug with the pen in it.
Turn right, go forward, and turn left to face the desk again.
Place the mug on the desk, in front of the keys and to the right of the book
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pen in it on the desk.
